{"tid":419703,"cid":1,"subCid":0,"title":"有無識法律嘅巴絲打喺度，可唔可以俾啲意見小弟⋯","createTime":"2017-09-30T17:00:04.000Z","updateTime":"2017-09-30T18:34:06.000Z","uid":80541,"like":12,"dislike":2,"uniUserReply":5,"replies":[{"pid":"6102a19df788d852d4f3ed6bc18da3eb24534559","tid":419703,"uid":80541,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-09-30T17:00:04.000Z","msg":"話說頭先喺巴士站等緊車，架車到嗰陣就有條友啱啱食完支煙之後打尖，跟住小弟就好聲叫佢排返隊，之後佢老婆排喺我前面話佢排緊，本身諗住就咁算，見佢老婆都係好聲好氣，點知條友突然間好激動，一個揮拳打中我左邊額頭，佢老婆有制止住佢，但係佢仲想打我，我見我好趕時間就上咗車，而條友同佢老婆就無上到車。各位巴絲打，其實我係咪應該報警？因為無表面傷痕，可唔可以告條友普通襲擊？<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/frown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n<img src=\"/assets/faces/big/good.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> 正評：去警局報案，打死都要告到條友。<br />\n<img src=\"/assets/faces/big/dislike.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> 負評：過咗去就算啦，一開始又唔落車報警。"},{"pid":"47b70998b546229df9d4a9bf083b4e41d73713b3","tid":419703,"uid":42910,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-09-30T17:01:28.000Z","msg":"香港法例212章侵害人身罪條例第40條"},{"pid":"3c764452492ebc517ef2d8474bdc9605051ca47e","tid":419703,"uid":80541,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-09-30T17:12:00.000Z","msg":"<blockquote>香港法例212章侵害人身罪條例第40條</blockquote><br />\n告入依條罪使唔使有傷口？<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/frown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"b383d97319fcbae10cc4e5eeec35f0d5371b21ca","tid":419703,"uid":13856,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-09-30T17:15:15.000Z","msg":"我見我好趕時間就上咗車<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"29ed1d8c31a1d291fa533b88926dc79b4bed212e","tid":419703,"uid":42910,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-09-30T17:16:11.000Z","msg":"<blockquote><blockquote>香港法例212章侵害人身罪條例第40條</blockquote><br />\n告入依條罪使唔使有傷口？<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/frown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /></blockquote><br />\n有傷口就39 襲擊導致他人受傷<br />\n呢條唔需要"},{"pid":"737b12ae5a9a5bbbe9859690667fa3b9ce2c217d","tid":419703,"uid":62504,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-09-30T17:16:46.000Z","msg":"冇相冇片冇證據 告條毛"},{"pid":"6d88f52ef4649a72621149cd2c433604021d8c0d","tid":419703,"uid":80541,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-09-30T17:18:38.000Z","msg":"<blockquote><blockquote><blockquote>香港法例212章侵害人身罪條例第40條</blockquote><br />\n告入依條罪使唔使有傷口？<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/frown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /></blockquote><br />\n有傷口就39 襲擊導致他人受傷<br />\n呢條唔需要</blockquote><br />\n但係我咩證據都無 如果睇到成件事嘅話應該得司機同埋幾個乘客<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/frown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"3a381b84c14a71abcb8a0bf69093c81ef9b8a524","tid":419703,"uid":80541,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-09-30T18:01:44.000Z","msg":"<blockquote>我見我好趕時間就上咗車<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /></blockquote><br />\n我都無眼睇自己<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"0e40d05eaffe0ed621cfb6bf6b2ab6eae50d9af4","tid":419703,"uid":37525,"like":0,"dislike":1,"score":-1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-09-30T18:29:12.000Z","msg":"<blockquote><blockquote>我見我好趕時間就上咗車<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /></blockquote><br />\n我都無眼睇自己<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /></blockquote><br />\n忍鳩咗佢算啦<br />\n痛一陣無嘢<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/angel.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n<br />\n<span style=\"font-size: small;\"><strong>咁都仲要開post問<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n仲搞埋啲濕鳩投票<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/dead.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />  </strong></span>"},{"pid":"3ea0e283d5c6c7edc1051c0159b8c46e2c120554","tid":419703,"uid":37525,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-09-30T18:34:06.000Z","msg":"而且你應該問有無警犬喺度<del><span style=\"font-size: x-small;\">mon post</span></del>下話<br />\n關法律JJ咩事？<br />\n你想民事佢claim醫藥費？<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/wonder2.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"}]}